				<h1>A Literary Road Trip Across America</h1>
		<h2>Where to Go and What to Read There</h2>
    <div class="inner">
		<div class="post_header_wrapper">
    				</div>
				<div class="author_info" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
			<div class="author_name">By&nbsp;<a href="https://lithub.com/author/literary-hub/" itemprop="url"><span itemprop="name">Literary&nbsp;Hub</span></a></div>
			<div class="author_hr"><hr/></div>
			<div class="publish_date">August 14, 2024</div>
		</div>
		<div class="social_links">
						<a href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?via=lithub&text=A+Literary+Road+Trip+Across+America&url=https%3A%2F%2Flithub.com%2Fa-literary-road-trip-across-america%2F"><span class="social_twitter"></span></a>
			<a href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Flithub.com%2Fa-literary-road-trip-across-america%2F&t=A+Literary+Road+Trip+Across+America"><span class="social_facebook"></span></a>
