<h2><strong>Literary Landmark:</strong></h2>
<p>Find your way to Nelle Harper Lee&#8217;s gravesite in Monroeville and leave a penny as tribute. [<a href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/Harper+Lee+Gravesite/@31.5301157,-87.3226509,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m6!3m5!1s0x88901d363119e227:0x4c701effad95cf58!8m2!3d31.5301158!4d-87.3177853!16s%2Fg%2F11h2pt3qcz?entry=ttu" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">MAP</a>]</p>
