<h2 style="text-align: center;"><strong>Poet of Note: </strong><a href="https://uas.alaska.edu/dir/z-arts-sciences-emeritus-ehhayes.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Ernestine Hayes</a></h2>
<p>The Tlingit poet and former state laureate&#8217;s &#8220;The Spoken Forest&#8221; is installed at Totem Bight State Park in Ketchikan. [<a class="waffle-rich-text-link external" href="https://goo.gl/maps/ytLiqE9nTJMfuJvCA" target="_blank">MAP</a>]</p>
