<h2><strong>Literary Landmark:</strong></h2>
<p>Jack London fans will find echoes of <a href="https://bookshop.org/a/132/9780804168854" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external"><em>The Call of the Wild</em></a> in Skagway, Alaska, where much of Buck&#8217;s story unfolds. [<a class="waffle-rich-text-link external" href="https://goo.gl/maps/AwPp8gkaf6zj2tTi6" target="_blank">MAP</a>]</p>
<h2><strong><a href="https://lithub.com/tag/alaska/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Read more on Literary Alaska</a></strong></h2>
