<h1>Colorado</h1>
<h2><strong>Spot to Read: </strong><a href="https://landlibrary.wordpress.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Rocky Mountain Land Library</a>, Fairplay</h2>
<p>An ongoing labor of love: this residential library is the result of a transformation of an abandoned ranch, celebrating nature and history. [<a class="waffle-rich-text-link external" href="https://goo.gl/maps/mZSWjFDxHWKxzbMQ7" target="_blank">MAP</a>]</p>
<h2><strong>What to Read There:</strong></h2>
<h4><a href="https://bookshop.org/a/132/9780375705854" class="external" target="_blank"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-attachment-id="240442" data-permalink="https://lithub.com/a-literary-road-trip-across-america/plainsong-2/" data-orig-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Plainsong.jpeg" data-orig-size="648,1000" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="Plainsong" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Plainsong-194x300.jpeg" data-large-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Plainsong.jpeg" class="size-medium wp-image-240442 alignleft" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Plainsong-194x300.jpeg" alt="Plainsong" width="194" height="300" srcset="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Plainsong-194x300.jpeg 194w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Plainsong-39x60.jpeg 39w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Plainsong-32x50.jpeg 32w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Plainsong.jpeg 648w" sizes="(max-width: 194px) 100vw, 194px" /></a></h4>
<h4 style="text-align: left;"><a href="https://bookshop.org/a/132/9780375705854" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external"><em>Plainsong</em></a><br />
by Kent Haruf</h4>
<p style="text-align: left;">This spare, gorgeous novel is set in the High Plains, in the fictional town of Holt. [<a class="waffle-rich-text-link external" href="https://goo.gl/maps/EWv4exS1Q3xEqtdn7" target="_blank">MAP</a>]</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h4><a href="https://bookshop.org/a/132/9780393357660" class="external" target="_blank"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-attachment-id="240443" data-permalink="https://lithub.com/a-literary-road-trip-across-america/deep-creek-by-pam-houston/" data-orig-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Deep-Creek-by-Pam-Houston.jpeg" data-orig-size="267,400" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="Deep Creek by Pam Houston" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Deep-Creek-by-Pam-Houston-200x300.jpeg" data-large-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Deep-Creek-by-Pam-Houston.jpeg" class="size-medium wp-image-240443 alignright" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Deep-Creek-by-Pam-Houston-200x300.jpeg" alt="Deep Creek by Pam Houston" width="200" height="300" srcset="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Deep-Creek-by-Pam-Houston-200x300.jpeg 200w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Deep-Creek-by-Pam-Houston-40x60.jpeg 40w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Deep-Creek-by-Pam-Houston-33x50.jpeg 33w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Deep-Creek-by-Pam-Houston.jpeg 267w" sizes="(max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px" /></a></h4>
<h4 style="text-align: right;"><a href="https://bookshop.org/a/132/9780393357660" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external"><em>Deep Creek</em></a><br />
by Pam Houston</h4>
<p style="text-align: right;">In these poignant essays, Houston revels in the Rockies’ beauty and chronicles the ways in which her 120-acre ranch high in the San Juan Mountains has healed and inspired her. [<a class="waffle-rich-text-link external" href="https://goo.gl/maps/9eruDP5AtrzFShs48" target="_blank">MAP</a>]</p>
<h1 style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-attachment-id="241522" data-permalink="https://lithub.com/a-literary-road-trip-across-america/quill-colorado/" data-orig-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/quill-colorado.png" data-orig-size="1200,250" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="quill colorado" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/quill-colorado-300x63.png" data-large-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/quill-colorado.png" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-241522" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/quill-colorado.png" alt="" width="1200" height="250" srcset="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/quill-colorado.png 1200w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/quill-colorado-300x63.png 300w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/quill-colorado-768x160.png 768w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/quill-colorado-60x13.png 60w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/quill-colorado-50x10.png 50w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></h1>
<h2><strong>Poet of Note: </strong><a href="https://camilledungy.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Camille Dungy</a></h2>
<p>The author of <a href="https://bookshop.org/a/132/9780819578563" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external"><em>Trophic Cascade</em></a> and distinguished professor at Colorado State University, Dungy released a new book of prose—<a href="https://bookshop.org/a/132/9781982195311" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external"><em>Soil: The Story of a Black Mother’s Garden</em></a>—in 2023. [<a class="waffle-rich-text-link external" href="https://goo.gl/maps/nT82mivdZGzuf6Cr9" target="_blank">MAP</a>]</p>
