<h2><strong>Literary Landmark: </strong><strong><a href="https://www.stanleyhotel.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">The Stanley Hotel</a>, Estes Park</strong></h2>
<p>The inspiration for <a href="https://bookshop.org/a/132/9780307743657" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external"><em>The Shining</em></a> came from a nightmare Stephen King had here, in room 217. [<a class="waffle-rich-text-link external" href="https://goo.gl/maps/cKv6p83dB5pTLav58" target="_blank">MAP</a>]</p>
