<h2><strong>Poet of Note: </strong><a href="https://www.antoinettebrimbell.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Antoinette Brim-Bell</a></h2>
<p>Brim-Bell, Connecticut&#8217;s 8th Poet Laureate, is the author of three collections: <a href="https://bookshop.org/a/132/9781945023057" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external"><em>These Women You Gave Me</em></a>, <em>Icarus in Love</em> and <em>Psalm of the Sunflower</em>. [<a class="waffle-rich-text-link external" href="https://goo.gl/maps/NiZbpE8kHb2ZPcaB7" target="_blank">MAP</a>]</p>
