<h2><strong>Literary Landmark: </strong><a href="https://poets.org/text/wallace-stevens-walk" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Wallace Stevens Walk</a>, Hartford</h2>
<p>Trace the 2.4 mile commute that Stevens made daily, from the house where his modernist verse was composed to his office at The Hartford. [<a class="waffle-rich-text-link external" href="https://goo.gl/maps/FXb4F26DJJ5t8AsK8" target="_blank">MAP</a>]</p>
