<h4 style="text-align: right;"><a href="https://cynthiaconnolly.square.site/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external"><em>Banned in D.C.</em></a><br />
by Cynthia Connolly</h4>
<p style="text-align: right;">A uniquely vivid, messy, and sweaty photographic document of D.C.&#8217;s vibrant early &#8217;80s punk underground, which remains a potent force shaping the city&#8217;s culture. [<a class="waffle-rich-text-link external" href="https://www.google.com/maps?output=search&amp;q=black+cat+dc&amp;entry=mc&amp;sa=X&amp;ved=2ahUKEwie8MH4kqX_AhXLAjQIHewtDa4Q0pQJegQIChAB" target="_blank">MAP</a>]</p>
