<h2><strong>Poet of Note: </strong><a href="https://www.poetryfoundation.org/people/sandra-beasley" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Sandra Beasley</a></h2>
<p>Beasley&#8217;s propulsive and visceral work often takes on national landmarks—from a bracing outsider&#8217;s perspective. [<a class="waffle-rich-text-link external" href="https://www.google.com/maps?output=search&amp;q=thomas+jefferson+memorial+washington+dc&amp;entry=mc&amp;sa=X&amp;ved=2ahUKEwjE-pPYk6X_AhVdIzQIHVCVAjQQ0pQJegQICRAB" target="_blank">MAP</a>]</p>
