<h2><strong>Literary Landmark: </strong><a href="https://www.loc.gov/research-centers/main/about-this-research-center/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Library of Congress Reading Room</a></h2>
<p>This soaring, cooly lit vault of national treasures is at the very heart of American letters. [<a class="waffle-rich-text-link external" href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/Library+of+Congress/@38.888684,-77.0069077,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m6!3m5!1s0x390feef68ef83a4d:0x46cbb296f4de3eec!8m2!3d38.888684!4d-77.004719!16zL20vMDRqcDI?entry=ttu" target="_blank">MAP</a>]</p>
