<h2>(Or Spend a Literary Long Weekend in <a href="https://lithub.com/how-to-spend-a-literary-long-weekend-in-atlanta/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Atlanta</a>)</h2>
<p><span id="hawaiian-goose"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-attachment-id="241359" data-permalink="https://lithub.com/a-literary-road-trip-across-america/hawaii-2-2/" data-orig-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/hawaii-2.jpg" data-orig-size="1200,780" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}" data-image-title="hawaii 2" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/hawaii-2-300x195.jpg" data-large-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/hawaii-2.jpg" class="aligncenter wp-image-241359" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/hawaii-2.jpg" alt="" width="780" height="507" srcset="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/hawaii-2.jpg 1200w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/hawaii-2-300x195.jpg 300w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/hawaii-2-768x499.jpg 768w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/hawaii-2-60x39.jpg 60w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/hawaii-2-50x33.jpg 50w" sizes="(max-width: 780px) 100vw, 780px" /></span></p>
<h1>Hawai&#8217;i</h1>
<h2><strong>Spot to Read: </strong><a href="https://ntbg.org/gardens/limahuli/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Limahuli Garden and Preserve</a></h2>
<p>One of only five National Tropical Botanical Gardens in the U.S.; the Canoe Garden features plants brought over by the region&#8217;s original Polynesian inhabitants. [<a class="waffle-rich-text-link external" href="https://goo.gl/maps/9LZgHs3ug38erANT7" target="_blank">MAP</a>]</p>
<h2><strong>What to Read There:</strong></h2>
<p><a href="https://bookshop.org/a/132/9780770436254" class="external" target="_blank"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-attachment-id="240514" data-permalink="https://lithub.com/a-literary-road-trip-across-america/this-is-paradise/" data-orig-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/this-is-paradise.jpeg" data-orig-size="267,400" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="this is paradise" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/this-is-paradise-200x300.jpeg" data-large-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/this-is-paradise.jpeg" class="size-medium wp-image-240514 alignleft" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/this-is-paradise-200x300.jpeg" alt="" width="200" height="300" srcset="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/this-is-paradise-200x300.jpeg 200w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/this-is-paradise-40x60.jpeg 40w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/this-is-paradise-33x50.jpeg 33w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/this-is-paradise.jpeg 267w" sizes="(max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px" /></a></p>
<h4 style="text-align: left;"><a href="https://bookshop.org/a/132/9780770436254" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external"><em>This Is Paradise</em></a><br />
by Kristiana Kahakauwila</h4>
<p style="text-align: left;">A collection of raw, vivid stories that invert traditional conceptions of paradise. [<a class="waffle-rich-text-link external" href="https://goo.gl/maps/fVxSvkfNeMHtvuWq8" target="_blank">MAP</a>] <em>See also</em>: <em>Sharks in the Time of Saviors</em> by Kawai Strong Washburn</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-attachment-id="240516" data-permalink="https://lithub.com/a-literary-road-trip-across-america/51c5q1dbael-_ac_uf10001000_ql80_/" data-orig-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/51C5Q1DBAEL._AC_UF10001000_QL80_.jpg" data-orig-size="652,1000" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="51C5Q1DBAEL._AC_UF1000,1000_QL80_" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/51C5Q1DBAEL._AC_UF10001000_QL80_-196x300.jpg" data-large-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/51C5Q1DBAEL._AC_UF10001000_QL80_.jpg" class="size-medium wp-image-240516 alignright" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/51C5Q1DBAEL._AC_UF10001000_QL80_-196x300.jpg" alt="" width="196" height="300" srcset="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/51C5Q1DBAEL._AC_UF10001000_QL80_-196x300.jpg 196w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/51C5Q1DBAEL._AC_UF10001000_QL80_-39x60.jpg 39w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/51C5Q1DBAEL._AC_UF10001000_QL80_-33x50.jpg 33w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/51C5Q1DBAEL._AC_UF10001000_QL80_.jpg 652w" sizes="(max-width: 196px) 100vw, 196px" /></p>
<h4 style="text-align: right;"><a href="https://bookshop.org/a/132/9781513271903" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external"><em>Hawai‘i’s Story</em> <em>by Hawai‘i’s Queen</em></a><br />
by Queen Lili’uokalani</h4>
<p style="text-align: right;">A stirring account—first published in 1898, five years after the overthrow of the Kingdom—written by the islands’ last monarch. [<a class="waffle-rich-text-link external" href="https://goo.gl/maps/HT6g1aWuqjvR95W38" target="_blank">MAP</a>]</p>
<h1 style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-attachment-id="241519" data-permalink="https://lithub.com/a-literary-road-trip-across-america/quill-arizona/" data-orig-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/quill-arizona.png" data-orig-size="1200,250" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="quill arizona" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/quill-arizona-300x63.png" data-large-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/quill-arizona.png" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-241519" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/quill-arizona.png" alt="" width="1200" height="250" srcset="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/quill-arizona.png 1200w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/quill-arizona-300x63.png 300w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/quill-arizona-768x160.png 768w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/quill-arizona-60x13.png 60w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/quill-arizona-50x10.png 50w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></h1>
<h2><strong>Poet of Note: </strong><a href="https://www.poetryfoundation.org/poets/w-s-merwin" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">W.S. Merwin</a></h2>
<p>Before his death, the former U.S. Poet Laureate, who was dedicated to the restoration of Maui&#8217;s rainforests, restored an old pineapple plantation to its original state. [<a class="waffle-rich-text-link external" href="https://goo.gl/maps/4CZLscfeGeXHtjLb6" target="_blank">MAP</a>]</p>
<p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-attachment-id="241201" data-permalink="https://lithub.com/a-literary-road-trip-across-america/talkstory/" data-orig-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/talkstory.png" data-orig-size="300,300" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="talkstory" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/talkstory.png" data-large-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/talkstory.png" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-241201" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/talkstory.png" alt="" width="300" height="300" srcset="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/talkstory.png 300w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/talkstory-150x150.png 150w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/talkstory-60x60.png 60w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/talkstory-109x109.png 109w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/talkstory-100x100.png 100w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/talkstory-50x50.png 50w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></p>
<h2><strong>Literary Landmark: </strong><a href="https://www.talkstorybookstore.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Talk Story Bookstore</a>, Hanapepe</h2>
<p>The westernmost bookstore in the U.S. has more than 150,000 titles on offer, including essential Kaua‘i reads. [<a class="waffle-rich-text-link external" href="https://goo.gl/maps/GhZFYvBtcdQEtPmZ8" target="_blank">MAP</a>]</p>
