<h4 style="text-align: right;"><a href="https://bookshop.org/a/132/9781608466290" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external"><em>All Our Relations</em></a><br />
by Winona LaDuke</h4>
<p style="text-align: right;">A formative work of Native resistance to oppression, written by an Anishinaabe environmental leader. [<a class="waffle-rich-text-link external" href="https://goo.gl/maps/5tDxAoQ8PmEZSjAaA" target="_blank">MAP</a>]</p>
