<h2><strong>Poet of Note: </strong><a href="http://www.joycesutphen.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Joyce Sutphen</a></h2>
<p>The state’s poet laureate grew up on a farm in St. Joseph and won the Minnesota Book Award for First Words. [<a class="waffle-rich-text-link external" href="https://goo.gl/maps/TyeXGYPGmV37xG3z5" target="_blank">MAP</a>]</p>
