<h2><strong>Literary Landmark: </strong><a href="https://www.mnbookarts.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Minnesota Center for Book Arts</a>, Minneapolis</h2>
<p>Papermaking, letterpress printing, and bookbinding all celebrate the book as an art form. Explore them here. [<a class="waffle-rich-text-link external" href="https://goo.gl/maps/hSZiShJfZP19Vtu49" target="_blank">MAP</a>]</p>
