-50x50.jpg 50w" sizes="(max-width: 769px) 100vw, 769px" /></span></p>
<h1>Mississippi</h1>
<h2><strong>Spot to Read: </strong><a href="https://rowanoak.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Rowan Oak</a>, Oxford</h2>
<p>Tour the house for inspiration, then find a spot among Faulkner&#8217;s gardens to read a while. [<a class="waffle-rich-text-link external" href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/Rowan+Oak/@34.3597974,-89.529579,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m6!3m5!1s0x88807abdd97e6665:0x5c366c79096fc6a7!8m2!3d34.3597975!4d-89.5247134!16zL20vMDVfcnBk?entry=ttu" target="_blank">MAP</a>]</p>
<h2><strong>What to Read There:</strong></h2>
<p><a href="https://bookshop.org/a/132/9781608196265" class="external" target="_blank"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-attachment-id="98786" data-permalink="https://lithub.com/7-novels-that-capture-the-pain-and-chaos-of-alcoholism/salvage-the-bones-jesmyn-ward/" data-orig-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Salvage-the-Bones-Jesmyn-Ward.jpg" data-orig-size="420,634" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="Salvage the Bones &#8211; Jesmyn Ward" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Salvage-the-Bones-Jesmyn-Ward-199x300.jpg" data-large-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Salvage-the-Bones-Jesmyn-Ward.jpg" class="size-medium wp-image-98786 alignleft" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Salvage-the-Bones-Jesmyn-Ward-199x300.jpg" alt="" width="199" height="300" srcset="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Salvage-the-Bones-Jesmyn-Ward-199x300.jpg 199w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Salvage-the-Bones-Jesmyn-Ward.jpg 420w" sizes="(max-width: 199px) 100vw, 199px" /></a></p>
<h4 style="text-align: left;"><a href="https://bookshop.org/a/132/9781608196265" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external"><em>Salvage the Bones</em></a><br />
by Jesmyn Ward</h4>
<p style="text-align: left;">Esch Batiste and her family prepare for Hurricane Katrina in fictional Bois Sauvage, Mississippi, in this National Book Award-winning novel from Ward, who also experienced Katrina. [<a class="waffle-rich-text-link external" href="https://goo.gl/maps/Qr3HF9rTDE9Atu6y9" target="_blank">MAP</a>]</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
