<h4 style="text-align: right;"><a href="https://bookshop.org/a/132/9781501125669" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external"><em>Heavy</em></a><br />
by Kiese Laymon</h4>
<p style="text-align: right;">Laymon&#8217;s powerful memoir about growing up as a Black man in Jackson, Mississippi reckons with harm in both public and private life. [<a class="waffle-rich-text-link external" href="https://goo.gl/maps/6wQF7yN2GeCHeQb97" target="_blank">MAP</a>]</p>
