<h1>Missouri</h1>
<h2><strong>Spot to Read: </strong>Loose Park Rose Garden, Kansas City</h2>
<p>A public horticultural respite brought to you by the Kansas City Rose Society. [<a class="waffle-rich-text-link external" href="https://goo.gl/maps/VuaSF5ZDXHJeegsU8" target="_blank">MAP</a>]</p>
<h2><strong>What to Read There:</strong></h2>
