<p>Living and teaching in St. Louis, Phillips recently took home a Pulitzer for his collection <em>Then the War: And Selected Poems</em>. [<a href="https://www.google.com/maps?sca_esv=28d067ce084b4185&amp;output=search&amp;q=st+louis+missouri&amp;source=lnms&amp;fbs=AEQNm0Aa4sjWe7Rqy32pFwRj0UkW1Cw7eydyNVBO-6Z_tTezO9uGZQMNvG3RJ7BbYkB3ncXLMK6NU6-Kc5qGYXNKgBkJXYGvrFTE1A1H0IvLaf7Vf45ji1d9M7KjF68JB3nF_ORNnOq2aZgkX3ucb0bq10hF_PORq6kr4TzHaQjkdEUPIjOzo1Gg_ZDYeEDxxuoqltQFQpab&amp;entry=mc&amp;ved=1t:200715&amp;ictx=111" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">MAP</a>]</p>
