<h4 style="text-align: right;"><a href="https://bookshop.org/a/132/9781250210692" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external"><em>Brothers on Three</em></a><br />
by Abe Streep</h4>
<p style="text-align: right;">More than a sports story (but an exciting one at that), this Montana Book Award winner follows two starters from the Arlee Warriors high school basketball team, who live and play on the Flathead Indian Reservation. [<a class="waffle-rich-text-link external" href="https://goo.gl/maps/YcJ6xHy5CLiE1mQk8" target="_blank">MAP</a>]</p>
