<h2><strong>Poet of Note: </strong>Henry Real Bird</h2>
<p>Crow Nation citizen, rancher, and former poet laureate, Henry Real Bird is known for traversing the state on horseback to craft an epic vision in verse. [<a class="waffle-rich-text-link external" href="https://www.google.com/maps?output=search&amp;q=crow+reservation+mt&amp;entry=mc&amp;sa=X&amp;ved=2ahUKEwiIgIS8l6X_AhXSMjQIHSLTBgEQ0pQJegQIDRAB" target="_blank">MAP</a>]</p>
