<h4 style="text-align: left;"><a href="https://bookshop.org/a/132/9780525562863" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external"><em>My Ántonia</em></a><br />
by Willa Cather</h4>
<p style="text-align: left;">The stories of immigrant Ántonia Shimerda and Jim Burden coalesce in Black Hawk, a town based on the author’s native Red Cloud. [<a class="waffle-rich-text-link external" href="https://goo.gl/maps/6WjA7Evqz8eRmCwE6" target="_blank">MAP</a>]</p>
