by Mari Sandoz</h4>
<p style="text-align: right;">Droughts, scarcity, and isolation are threaded through oral histories passed down from a pioneer father. [<a class="waffle-rich-text-link external" href="https://goo.gl/maps/22ws58D17djk5QRB8" target="_blank">MAP</a>]</p>
