<h2><strong>Poet of Note: </strong><a href="https://www.tedkooser.net/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Ted Kooser</a></h2>
<p>His poetic ode to the state appropriately begins with “the gravel road rides with a slow gallop over the fields.” [<a class="waffle-rich-text-link external" href="https://goo.gl/maps/srrvhJ4fsYVX8nXV6" target="_blank">MAP</a>]</p>
