<h1>Nevada</h1>
<h2><strong>Spot to Read: </strong><a href="https://www.peppermilllasvegas.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">The Peppermill</a></h2>
<p>Low neon lighting and purple plush booths serve as the backdrop for this Reno lounge, which slings breakfast and cocktails any time—perfect for 3 a.m. or p.m.—and which was a longtime favorite of MacArthur-winning art critic and writer Dave Hickey. [<a class="waffle-rich-text-link external" href="https://goo.gl/maps/jx5mVYMXp8SbD58M7" target="_blank">MAP</a>]</p>
