<h2><strong>Poet of Note: </strong><a href="https://www.poetryfoundation.org/poets/william-carlos-williams" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">William Carlos Williams</a></h2>
<p>A practicing physician for more than 40 years, Williams&#8217; empathic and honest verse has made him a household name in every state. [<a class="waffle-rich-text-link external" href="https://goo.gl/maps/P34MG3PCdqSRrs4j8" target="_blank">MAP</a>]</p>
<p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-attachment-id="241238" data-permalink="https://lithub.com/a-literary-road-trip-across-america/ginsberg-4/" data-orig-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/ginsberg.png" data-orig-size="300,300" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="ginsberg" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/ginsberg.png" data-large-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/ginsberg.png" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-241238" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/ginsberg.png" alt="" width="300" height="300" srcset="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/ginsberg.png 300w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/ginsberg-150x150.png 150w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/ginsberg-60x60.png 60w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/ginsberg-109x109.png 109w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/ginsberg-100x100.png 100w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/ginsberg-50x50.png 50w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></p>
<h2><strong>Literary Landmark: </strong>Allen Ginsberg’s Grave, Newark</h2>
<p>Pay homage to Allen Ginsberg, poet laureate of the Beat generation, at his gravesite at B’Nai Israel Cemetery. [<a class="waffle-rich-text-link external" href="https://goo.gl/maps/fBN2cUibMV8wHfmp7" target="_blank">MAP</a>]</p>
<h2><strong><a href="https://lithub.com/tag/New-jersey/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Read more on Literary New Jersey</a></strong></h2>
