<h2><strong>Poet of Note: </strong><a href="https://www.abdurraqib.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Hanif Abdurraqib</a></h2>
<p>The decorated poet and essayist, born and raised in Columbus, was recently awarded a MacArthur &#8220;Genius&#8221; Grant. [<a class="waffle-rich-text-link external" href="https://goo.gl/maps/Qh6vNu43hue7npXK6" target="_blank">MAP</a>]</p>
<h2><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-attachment-id="241242" data-permalink="https://lithub.com/a-literary-road-trip-across-america/sa/" data-orig-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/sa.png" data-orig-size="300,300" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="sa" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/sa.png" data-large-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/sa.png" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-241242" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/sa.png" alt="" width="300" height="300" srcset="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/sa.png 300w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/sa-150x150.png 150w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/sa-60x60.png 60w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/sa-109x109.png 109w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/sa-100x100.png 100w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/sa-50x50.png 50w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></h2>
<h2><strong>Literary Landmark: </strong>Camden</h2>
<p>Visit the hometown of Sherwood Anderson, the author of small-town classic <a href="https://bookshop.org/a/132/9780140186550" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external"><em>Winesburg, Ohio</em></a>. [<a class="waffle-rich-text-link external" href="https://goo.gl/maps/gNxDRr5BwNNkg6Au6" target="_blank">MAP</a>]</p>
