<h1>Tennessee</h1>
<h2><strong>Spot to Read: </strong>Centennial Park, Nashville</h2>
<p>Visit this 132-acre oasis in Nashville’s West End. [<a class="waffle-rich-text-link external" href="https://goo.gl/maps/2e4VyCauuCvXpLvy5" target="_blank">MAP</a>}</p>
<h2><strong>What to Read There:</strong></h2>
<h4><a href="https://bookshop.org/a/132/9780143105718" class="external" target="_blank"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-attachment-id="240841" data-permalink="https://lithub.com/a-literary-road-trip-across-america/james-agee-a-death-in-the-family/" data-orig-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/james-agee-a-death-in-the-family.jpeg" data-orig-size="653,1000" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="james agee a death in the family" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/james-agee-a-death-in-the-family-196x300.jpeg" data-large-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/james-agee-a-death-in-the-family.jpeg" class="size-medium wp-image-240841 alignleft" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/james-agee-a-death-in-the-family-196x300.jpeg" alt="" width="196" height="300" srcset="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/james-agee-a-death-in-the-family-196x300.jpeg 196w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/james-agee-a-death-in-the-family-39x60.jpeg 39w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/james-agee-a-death-in-the-family-33x50.jpeg 33w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/james-agee-a-death-in-the-family.jpeg 653w" sizes="(max-width: 196px) 100vw, 196px" /></a></h4>
<h4 style="text-align: left;"><a href="https://bookshop.org/a/132/9780143105718" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external"><em>A Death in the Family</em></a><br />
by James Agee</h4>
<p style="text-align: left;">Dual tragedies shape this autobiographical novel, winner of the Pulitzer Prize. [<a class="waffle-rich-text-link external" href="https://goo.gl/maps/AUaDsUPWvzw7Egcr9" target="_blank">MAP</a>]</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><a href="https://bookshop.org/a/132/9781631491931" class="external" target="_blank"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-attachment-id="240842" data-permalink="https://lithub.com/a-literary-road-trip-across-america/dreams-to-remember/" data-orig-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Dreams-to-Remember.jpeg" data-orig-size="266,400" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="Dreams to Remember" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Dreams-to-Remember-200x300.jpeg" data-large-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Dreams-to-Remember.jpeg" class="size-medium wp-image-240842 alignright" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Dreams-to-Remember-200x300.jpeg" alt="" width="200" height="300" srcset="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Dreams-to-Remember-200x300.jpeg 200w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Dreams-to-Remember-40x60.jpeg 40w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Dreams-to-Remember-33x50.jpeg 33w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Dreams-to-Remember.jpeg 266w" sizes="(max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px" /></a></p>
<h4 style="text-align: right;"><a href="https://bookshop.org/a/132/9781631491931" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external"><em>Dreams to Remember: Otis Redding, Stax Records, and the Transformation of Southern Soul</em></a><br />
by Mark Ribowsky</h4>
<p style="text-align: right;">The Stax Records story is a window into a transformative era in American Music and properly celebrates the iconic Memphis record label. [<a href="https://www.google.com/maps?sca_esv=c839f9702c677c11&amp;output=search&amp;q=memphis+tennessee&amp;source=lnms&amp;fbs=AEQNm0Aa4sjWe7Rqy32pFwRj0UkW1Cw7eydyNVBO-6Z_tTezO9uGZQMNvG3RJ7BbYkB3ncXLMK6NU6-Kc5qGYXNKgBkJXYGvrFTE1A1H0IvLaf7Vf45ji1d9M7KjF68JB3nF_ORNnOq2aZgkX3ucb0bq10hF_PORq6kr4TzHaQjkdEUPIjOzo1Gg_ZDYeEDxxuoqltQFQpab&amp;entry=mc&amp;ved=1t:200715&amp;ictx=111" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">MAP</a>]</p>
<h1 style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-attachment-id="241519" data-permalink="https://lithub.com/a-literary-road-trip-across-america/quill-arizona/" data-orig-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/quill-arizona.png" data-orig-size="1200,250" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="quill arizona" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/quill-arizona-300x63.png" data-large-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/quill-arizona.png" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-241519" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/quill-arizona.png" alt="" width="1200" height="250" srcset="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/quill-arizona.png 1200w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/quill-arizona-300x63.png 300w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/quill-arizona-768x160.png 768w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/quill-arizona-60x13.png 60w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/quill-arizona-50x10.png 50w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></h1>
<h2><strong>Poet of Note: </strong><a href="https://carolinerandallwilliams.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Caroline Randall Williams</a></h2>
<p>Her first collection of poetry reimagines the life of Shakespeare’s mysterious “Dark Lady.” [<a class="waffle-rich-text-link external" href="https://goo.gl/maps/3VS9nxaQq9vyzQGA6" target="_blank">MAP</a>]</p>
