<h2><strong>Literary Landmark: </strong><a href="https://www.parnassusbooks.net/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Parnassus Books</a>, Nashville</h2>
<p>Ann Patchett’s cherished shop opened in 2011. [<a class="waffle-rich-text-link external" href="https://goo.gl/maps/ag3mBzwfxnH1NP4x5" target="_blank">MAP</a>]</p>
