<h1>Wisconsin</h1>
<h2><strong>Spot to Read: </strong><a href="https://www.boswellbooks.com/opening-letter-0" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Boswell Books</a>, Milwaukee</h2>
<p>This East Side indie book enclave is a community treasure. [<a class="waffle-rich-text-link external" href="https://goo.gl/maps/Tg4xig6cgEL9ZqYd8" target="_blank">MAP</a>]</p>
<h2><strong>What to Read There:</strong></h2>
<h4><a href="https://bookshop.org/a/132/9780316126670" class="external" target="_blank"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-attachment-id="99413" data-permalink="https://lithub.com/a-campus-novel-for-every-kind-of-back-to-schooler/29-art-of-fielding-w330-h412/" data-orig-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/29-art-of-fielding.w330.h412.jpg" data-orig-size="300,463" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}" data-image-title="29-art-of-fielding.w330.h412" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/29-art-of-fielding.w330.h412-194x300.jpg" data-large-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/29-art-of-fielding.w330.h412.jpg" class="size-medium wp-image-99413 alignleft" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/29-art-of-fielding.w330.h412-194x300.jpg" alt="Chad Harbach, The Art of Fielding" width="194" height="300" srcset="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/29-art-of-fielding.w330.h412-194x300.jpg 194w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/29-art-of-fielding.w330.h412.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 194px) 100vw, 194px" /></a></h4>
<h4 style="text-align: left;"><a href="https://bookshop.org/a/132/9780316126670" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external"><em>The Art of Fielding</em></a><br />
by Chad Harbach</h4>
<p style="text-align: left;">In which the Harpooners—a baseball team at Westish College, a fictional school on the shores of Lake Michigan—embark on a Melville-influenced season. [<a class="waffle-rich-text-link external" href="https://goo.gl/maps/37A6YCupXHSGvCxj9" target="_blank">MAP</a>]</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><a href="https://bookshop.org/a/132/9780826321930" class="external" target="_blank"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-attachment-id="240854" data-permalink="https://lithub.com/a-literary-road-trip-across-america/wisconsin-death-trip-by-michael-lesy/" data-orig-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Wisconsin-Death-Trip-by-Michael-Lesy.jpeg" data-orig-size="1295,1000" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}" data-image-title="Wisconsin Death Trip by Michael Lesy" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Wisconsin-Death-Trip-by-Michael-Lesy-300x232.jpeg" data-large-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Wisconsin-Death-Trip-by-Michael-Lesy-1240x958.jpeg" class="size-medium wp-image-240854 alignright" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Wisconsin-Death-Trip-by-Michael-Lesy-300x232.jpeg" alt="" width="300" height="232" srcset="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Wisconsin-Death-Trip-by-Michael-Lesy-300x232.jpeg 300w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Wisconsin-Death-Trip-by-Michael-Lesy-1240x958.jpeg 1240w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Wisconsin-Death-Trip-by-Michael-Lesy-768x593.jpeg 768w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Wisconsin-Death-Trip-by-Michael-Lesy-60x46.jpeg 60w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Wisconsin-Death-Trip-by-Michael-Lesy-50x39.jpeg 50w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Wisconsin-Death-Trip-by-Michael-Lesy.jpeg 1295w" sizes="(